    },
    {
      "review_id": "BylH3HnQnm",
      "rebuttal_id": "HJec4jK_R7",
      "sentence_index": 11,
      "text": "We show that the rate of convergence of the RBM is geometric in the number of sampling steps, and that the combined RBM will have a convergence rate bounded by the sum of the convergence rates of the individual RBMs.",
